                  <additions>
                  <list>
                    <item xml:id = "a01">
                      <desc>
                        <locus target = "#175r"/> <foreign xml:lang = "gez">አስማት፡</foreign> prayer against the enemy, copied for <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ወልደ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡</foreign>
                      </desc>
                      </item>
                    <item xml:id = "a02">
                      <desc>Some psalms are marked with qəb‘ that is serially numbered. It must have been used as a prayer on remedial oil.
                        Some versicles are encircled in ink. These were apparently the ones that are used in the liturgy.</desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id = "a03">
                      <desc type = "OwnershipNote">
                        <locus target = "#1ir"/> The name <foreign xml:lang = "gez">አብርሃ፡ ከሳይ፡</foreign>, possible a one-time owner of the manuscript, and scribbling, in a crude hand.
                        </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id = "a04">
                      <desc>
                      Overlooked lines of text are added interlinearly (<locus target = "#72r #95r #104v #141r #143r #147v #148r #153r"/>)
                      </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id = "a05">
                      <desc type = "OwnershipNote">
                        Note of ownership by <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ቄስ፡ ሀደረ፡ አብርሃ፡</foreign> <locus target = "#29v"/>, and <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ሀለቀ፡ ተስፋይ፡</foreign> <locus target = "#40v"/>, with the name of the original owner on <locus target = "#158v"/> erased.
                      </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id = "a06">
                      <desc>
                        <locus target = "#86r #158v"/> The name of <foreign xml:lang = "gez">አለቀ፡ ገብረ፡ ጸድቅ፡</foreign> of <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ቤተል አብርሃም፡</foreign>
                      </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id = "a07">
                      <desc>
                      <locus target = "#158v #175r #175v"/> words and phrases copied in crude hands
                      </desc>
                    </item>
